message.body: So don't buy honey or cinnamon ...I have lots & I'll give you some.
Also that book, haha. Embrace the woo!

It is kind of wooey...I started reading it but I just can't be serious about it...cultural differences I guess. So Molly had her students bring in honey & cinnamon to make applesauce & she gave me a bunch to share. They're all unopened & I checked exp dates!
